{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, we-- we weren't that this is the last week, but we knew that things are coming up very soon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a cousin of my, who already, weeks before, tried to organize a-- like a partisan-- and he talked to some young men-- he used to come into-- to the camp, the concentration camp at night, and they used-- he used to talk [? cover ?] with certain-- with men that he knew them.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and to organize that they would escape during the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and he made already-- sort of-- he looked around in-- in the forest, a place that we would be able to-- to-- to go there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He wasn't really in camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- I don't know what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- that time, he lived in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A young boy, he was only 19 or 20.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His Jewish name, Abraham.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we called him [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very nice, handsome young guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a lot of courage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, he just-- he really wanted to do anything possible to-- to-- not to let us, you know, just be killed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he organized quite a few young men, strong, nice guys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he-- and-- woman, he didn't want-- I mean, he just wanted men that can fight back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But whoever had a sister, a girlfriend, a wife, or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyway, I was his cousin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he took me that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did he get in touch with you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to come in, like I said, during the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And being that we were on this-- on this field, in the last-- the last weeks, we were practically sleeping every night there.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
